<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungkham ni um intin,
 Buoina phat um mahleh;
 Kipak zel ka eina sam ui,
 Angelte lenna gamah.

[V2]
 Angelte lenna gamah,
 Gamla tak gam nuomah;
 Phat kipahum ah chawl taitiu,
 Angelte lenna gam ah.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa chuh ka hatna,
 Ei puipa - Aksi chuh;
 Zie gam chuh ei puitung ina,
 Angelte lenna gam ah.

[V4]
 3. Gamla tak gam nuom ah,
 Ka chen na'ng In a um;
 Lallukhuk kei di'ng in a um,
 Angelte lenna gam ah.

[V5]
 4. Van In zuon in ka chieh,
 Buoina pel pai tang ka;
 Van In bit takin tung ing ka,
 Angelte lenna gamah.</lyrics>
<title>WHERE GOD AND THE ANGELS ARE</title>
<hymn_number>395</hymn_number>
</song>